## ⚙️ Local Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/FerdiBoy01/HireReady-AI.git
cd HireReady-AI
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Run backend:

```bash
cd backend
npm run dev
```

Run frontend:

```bash
cd frontend
npm run dev
```

